'''''Bhagavathipuram Railway Gate''''' is a [[1983 in film|1983]] [[Tamil language|Tamil]]  [[Cinema of India|Indian]] [[feature film]] [[Film director|directed]] by Selvaraj for M.Balasubramananian's Karur B.S.Films. The film stars [[Karthik Muthuraman|Karthik]] and [[Rajalakshmi (actress)|Rajalakshmi]] in the lead role.<ref>{{cite web|title=Bhagavathipuram Railway Gate LP Vinyl Records|url=http://musicalaya.net/imgviewer.php?mod=lpcovers/129/3/1/1|publisher=musicalaya|accessdate=2014-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140502003246/http://musicalaya.net/imgviewer.php?mod=lpcovers%2F129%2F3%2F1%2F1|archive-date=2 May 2014|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

